<paragraph blockId="9.[94,719,218,595]" pageId="9" pageNumber="10">
Males of 
<taxonomicName authority="Biffi &amp; Constantin, 2018" authorityName="Biffi &amp; Constantin" authorityYear="2018" box="[231,379,282,307]" class="Insecta" family="Cantharidae" genus="Macromalthinus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="10" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="orapuensis" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis box="[231,379,282,307]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="10">M. orapuensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[385,469,282,307]" pageId="9" pageNumber="10" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
differ from 
<taxonomicName authority="(Pic)" baseAuthorityName="Pic" class="Insecta" family="Cantharidae" genus="Macromalthinus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="10" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="maximiceps">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="10">M. maximiceps</emphasis>
(Pic)
</taxonomicName>
in the narrower and less concave frons between the eyes, antennomeres IV-V not widened and the different aedeagus. 
<taxonomicName authority="Biffi &amp; Constantin, 2018" authorityName="Biffi &amp; Constantin" authorityYear="2018" box="[256,553,378,403]" class="Insecta" family="Cantharidae" genus="Macromalthinus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="10" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="orapuensis" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis box="[256,553,378,403]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="10">Macromalthinus orapuensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[559,643,378,403]" pageId="9" pageNumber="10" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
is similar to 
<taxonomicName authority="Biffi &amp; Constantin, 2018" authorityName="Biffi &amp; Constantin" authorityYear="2018" box="[169,322,410,435]" class="Insecta" family="Cantharidae" genus="Macromalthinus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="10" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="guyanensis" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis box="[169,322,410,435]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="10">M. guyanensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[330,417,410,435]" pageId="9" pageNumber="10" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
and differs from the latter in the different apical edge of the aedeagus. Females of 
<taxonomicName authority="Biffi &amp; Constantin, 2018" authorityName="Biffi &amp; Constantin" authorityYear="2018" box="[94,243,474,499]" class="Insecta" family="Cantharidae" genus="Macromalthinus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="10" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="orapuensis" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis box="[94,243,474,499]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="10">M. orapuensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[250,336,474,499]" pageId="9" pageNumber="10" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
differ by the distal margin of ventrite VII projected at middle and with a pair of lobes at apex (slightly projected, nearly straight in 
<taxonomicName authority="Biffi &amp; Constantin, 2018" authorityName="Biffi &amp; Constantin" authorityYear="2018" box="[566,718,538,563]" class="Insecta" family="Cantharidae" genus="Macromalthinus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="10" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="guyanensis" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis box="[566,718,538,563]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="10">M. guyanensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[94,178,570,595]" pageId="9" pageNumber="10" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
and concave in 
<taxonomicName box="[355,515,570,595]" class="Insecta" family="Cantharidae" genus="Macromalthinus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="10" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="maximiceps">
<emphasis box="[355,515,570,595]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="10">M. maximiceps</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
).
</paragraph>
